The paper deals with safe navigation of Micro Aerial Vehicles (MAVs) using onboard sensors, which falls under the category of Robotics (cs.RO). The paper also involves perception and reaction to dynamic objects, which can be related to Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Control Systems (cs.SY). The approach presented in the paper involves planning and optimization, which can be related to Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG).
